 - g_mount_guess_content_type_sync: synchronous version of
   g_mount_guess_content_type
 - GEmblem: A GIcon implementation that adds emblem-related
   metadata to icons
 - GEmblemedIcon: A GIcon implementation that can add emblems
   to icons

