Overview of Changes from GLib 2.13.7 to GLib 2.14.0
===================================================

* Last-minute API additions:
 - Make g_unichar_combining_class public
 - Add goffset type, add G_MAXSSIZE and G_MINSSIZE

* Update PCRE to 7.2

* Bugs fixed:
