Overview of Changes from GLib 2.3.3 to GLib 2.3.5
=================================================

* Make glib-mkenums parse initializers with macros. [Matthias Clasen, muppet]
* Respect locale era in g_date_set_parse(). [Theppitak Karoonboonyanan] 
